| Cold start (ms)     | 850      | 920     | +8.2%      | WARN     |
| TTI (ms)            | 1450     | 1500    | +3.4%      | stable   |
| FPS scroll (median) | 58       | 56      | -2 fps     | stable   |
| Jank rate           | 2.1%     | 4.8%    | +2.7 pp    | FAIL     |
| Peak memory (MB)    | 180      | 210     | +16.7%     | WARN     |

## Failing metric: jank-rate

- Scenario: ProfileScreen scroll x 10
- Root cause: likely the new image-cache eviction policy from commit `abc123`
- Frame samples: `mobile/perf/{date}/jank-frames-{n}.json`
- Recommendation: revert eviction change or move image decoding off the main thread.

## Trace artifacts
